snippet.title: SJSM: The Doll House - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming October 1st 2020,

A new DLC for the original free version of Spooky's Jump Scare Mansion, and coming to the HD release of SJSM as a free content update.

The DLC version is made on the original engine that SJSM used, and the HD release is made to follow it as close as possible.

I know it's a bizarre release in this way, but I tried my hardest to make the DLC version as good as I could and push the limits of the engine and the AMG team are trying their hardest to remake it faithfully in the HD version and utilize the extra features of their engine.

Thanks for all the support over the years, I'm eagerly looking forward to the release.
